{"tid":723320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[噓，大把位呀] 今次到59M 九巴關愛座現7cm鐵針","createTime":"2018-06-30T09:47:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T06:54:56.000Z","uid":28435,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"8bed5d22677ec04fba031d1b9a22851c0dd8db0a","tid":723320,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:47:18.000Z","msg":"再有九巴暗藏鐵針！下午4時許，一名乘客乘搭59M線九巴返回屯門碼頭總站後，發現下層其中一個關愛座位上，放了約7厘米長的鐵針，於是通知車長，車長立即報案。警員接報到場，封鎖涉事巴士調查。<br />\n<br />\n連同今日在內，九巴在4日內已發生第5宗座位暗藏鐵針，事件導致兩名女乘客被刺傷臀部及大腿。九巴59M號路線來往屯門碼頭至荃灣站總站。"},{"pid":"965af3df0e675571ec9638550c57e0bbbf62d1d8","tid":723320,"uid":29070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:50:25.000Z","msg":"係咪打算條條九巴線都落針<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1eec9f0872950a8ad035391bf626c620d9825ca","tid":723320,"uid":6222,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:54:51.000Z","msg":"仲未破到案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n掛住部署7 1 點毆D示威者無人查案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8110b7bd92482ee75564af9a91cadc1f5457e741","tid":723320,"uid":78399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:56:29.000Z","msg":"我估好快九巴就加裝多幾個CCTV"},{"pid":"ef17a6607fd91dd98997b5d0a6156685381376b9","tid":723320,"uid":96743,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T10:54:55.000Z","msg":"狗鐵咪醒囉 鐵櫈放唔到針"},{"pid":"2d0ef35d5f30218571393dc1a31fc7c14870e883","tid":723320,"uid":91813,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:46:16.000Z","msg":"所以話mtr有先見之明"},{"pid":"fadaa66b2f04c9ca36b206fdf0e1bc55dba438aa","tid":723320,"uid":71433,"like":10,"dislike":7,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T11:49:40.000Z","msg":"大家真係小心d<br />\n前幾日我女朋友話個處女膜就係比呢d鐵針督穿咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\